data.description: Nice one owner D20 home with 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms and 2,685 square feet. New carpet throughout the home and all new bathroom light fixtures. The living room/dining room combo has vaulted ceilings and a bay window. The kitchen is bright and open to the family room which has a wood-burning fireplace and built-ins. The kitchen has stainless-steel appliances including a glass-top stove. The family room walks out to a lovely sunroom and a nice-sized deck with mountain views. That master bedroom has an attached bath with a double vanity. The finished basement has an additional family room/rec room, a bedroom, a full bathroom and a flex room that is currently being used as an exercise room. Plenty of room for RV parking.
